title: Garmin DriveAssist: Camera-assistance Behind the Wheel
description:
Meet the new Garmin DriveAssist. This GPS navigator watches out for you with a built-in dash cam that automatically records your drive and saves footage on impact. It also features Forward Collision and Lane Departure Warnings, Garage Park Assist and so much more.

• 5.0-inch GPS auto navigator with built-in dash cam that records your drive and saves files on impact
• Detailed maps of North America with free lifetime1 updates; plus built-in Wi-Fi for easy map and software updates
• Live Traffic and Live Parking information saves drivers time and hassle
• Forward Collision and Lane Departure Warnings
• Garmin Real Vision shows camera view during lane changes or when approaching select destinations; and an arrow points exactly where you need to go
• Garage Park Assist guides to your desired stopping point within your saved garage location
• Hands-free Bluetooth calling, voice-activated navigation, and smart notifications
